Jsi docela zvrhlý!

114
00:09:16,170 --> 00:09:17,240
Takaoni! (Horský démon)

115
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:18,780
<i>Už je to tady!</i>

116
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:27,790
